text: Rachel Elizabeth Brosnahan (born July 12, 1990) is an American-British actress. She is known for appearing as Miriam "Midge" Maisel in Prime Video's period comedy series The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel. She won a Primetime Emmy Award in 2018 and two Golden Globe Awards in 2018 and 2019. She will play Lois Lane in the DC Universe, starting with the upcoming movie Superman (2025).
